<p data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">In the context of Next.js, runtime refers to the set of libraries, APIs, and general functionality available to your code during execution.<span lang="zh-CN" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><br><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1">在 Next.js 的上下文中，运行时是指代码在执行期间可用的一组库、API 和常规功能。</span></span></span></p>
<p data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">On the server, there are two runtimes where parts of your application code can be rendered:<span lang="zh-CN" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><br><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1">在服务器上，有两个运行时，可以在其中呈现部分应用程序代码：</span></span></span></p>
<ul data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">
<li data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">The <strong data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">Node.js Runtime</strong> (default) has access to all Node.js APIs and compatible packages from the ecosystem.<span lang="zh-CN" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><br><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1">Node.js 运行时（默认）可以访问生态系统中的所有 Node.js API 和兼容包。</span></span></span></li>
<li data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">The <strong data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">Edge Runtime</strong> is based on <a href="https://nextjs.org/docs/app/api-reference/edge" data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">Web APIs</a>.<span lang="zh-CN" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><br><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1">Edge 运行时基于 Web API。</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
