<h3 id="edge-runtime" data-docs-heading="" data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06"><a href="#edge-runtime" data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06">Edge Runtime<span lang="zh-CN" data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1">&nbsp;</span><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1"><span data-immersive-translate-translation-element-mark="1">Edge 运行时</span></span></span><span data-immersive-translate-effect="1" data-immersive_translate_walked="01a740c1-0749-4e40-b96a-60a93aec3d06"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" height="0.7em" width="0.7em">
